---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>Fig - Visual Claude Code Configuration</title>
		<meta name="description" content="A native macOS application for managing Claude Code configuration. Stop hand-editing scattered JSON files." />
		<meta property="og:title" content="Fig - Visual Claude Code Configuration" />
		<meta property="og:description" content="A native macOS application for managing Claude Code configuration." />
		<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/fig/favicon.png" />
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/fig/apple-touch-icon.png" />
		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			:root {
				--fig-purple: #6b3fa0;
				--fig-purple-dark: #4a2870;
				--fig-purple-light: #9b6dd7;
				--fig-lavender: #f3e8ff;
				--fig-green: #4a8c5c;
				--fig-orange: #e87f3a;
				--fig-bg: #ffffff;
				--fig-text: #1a1a2e;
				--fig-text-muted: #555;
				--fig-card-bg: #ffffff;
				--fig-card-border: #e8e0f0;
				--fig-code-bg: #1e1e2e;
			}

			@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
				:root {
					--fig-purple: #9b6dd7;
					--fig-purple-dark: #e8d5ff;
					--fig-purple-light: #6b3fa0;
					--fig-lavender: #2d1650;
					--fig-bg: #121218;
					--fig-text: #e8e0f0;
					--fig-text-muted: #a0a0b0;
					--fig-card-bg: #1a1a28;
					--fig-card-border: #2d2d40;
				}
			}

			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
				background: var(--fig-bg);
				color: var(--fig-text);
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			a {
				color: var(--fig-purple);
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}

			/* Nav */
			nav {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
			}

			nav .logo {
				font-weight: 700;
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: var(--fig-purple);
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			.nav-logo-img {
				width: 28px;
				height: 28px;
				object-fit: contain;
			}

			nav .nav-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				list-style: none;
			}

			nav .nav-links a {
				color: var(--fig-text-muted);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}

			nav .nav-links a:hover {
				color: var(--fig-purple);
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			/* Hero */
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.hero-logo {
				width: 160px;
				height: auto;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.hero h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				color: var(--fig-text);
			}

			.hero h1 span {
				color: var(--fig-purple);
			}

			.hero p {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: var(--fig-text-muted);
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto 2rem;
			}

			.hero-actions {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1rem;
				justify-content: center;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
			}

			.btn {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				transition: opacity 0.2s;
			}

			.btn:hover {
				opacity: 0.9;
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.btn-primary {
				background: var(--fig-purple);
				color: #fff;
			}

			.btn-secondary {
				border: 2px solid var(--fig-purple);
				color: var(--fig-purple);
			}

			/* Features */
			.features {
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
			}

			.features h2 {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.feature-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
			}

			.feature-card {
				background: var(--fig-card-bg);
				border: 1px solid var(--fig-card-border);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
			}

			.feature-card h3 {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			.feature-card p {
				color: var(--fig-text-muted);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}

			.feature-icon {
				font-size: 1.3rem;
			}

			/* Install */
			.install {
				max-width: 700px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
			}

			.install h2 {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.code-block {
				background: var(--fig-code-bg);
				color: #cdd6f4;
				border-radius: 10px;
				padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
				font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', 'Consolas', monospace;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
				overflow-x: auto;
			}

			.code-block .comment {
				color: #6c7086;
			}

			/* Footer */
			footer {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
				color: var(--fig-text-muted);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--fig-card-border);
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 2rem auto 0;
			}

			footer .footer-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				justify-content: center;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
				list-style: none;
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.hero h1 {
					font-size: 1.75rem;
				}

				.hero p {
					font-size: 1.05rem;
				}

				.feature-grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<nav>
			<div class="logo"><img src="/fig/fig-logo.png" alt="Fig logo" class="nav-logo-img" /> Fig</div>
			<ul class="nav-links">
				<li><a href="/fig/getting-started/">Docs</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://github.com/utensils/fig">GitHub</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>

		<section class="hero">
			<img src="/fig/fig-logo.png" alt="Fig logo" class="hero-logo" />
			<h1>A visual interface for <span>Claude Code</span> configuration</h1>
			<p>
				Stop hand-editing scattered JSON files. Fig discovers your projects
				and lets you manage settings, MCP servers, and hooks from one native
				macOS app.
			</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<a href="/fig/getting-started/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/utensils/fig" class="btn btn-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="features">
			<h2>Features</h2>
			<div class="feature-grid">
				<div class="feature-card">
					<h3><span class="feature-icon">üîç</span> Project Discovery</h3>
					<p>Automatically finds your Claude Code projects from ~/.claude.json and common development directories.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<h3><span class="feature-icon">üîå</span> MCP Server Management</h3>
					<p>Add, edit, and copy MCP servers between projects with a visual interface. Supports both stdio and SSE transports.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<h3><span class="feature-icon">ü™ù</span> Visual Hook Composer</h3>
					<p>Configure Claude Code hooks without writing JSON by hand. Set up PreToolUse, PostToolUse, and other event handlers visually.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<h3><span class="feature-icon">‚úÖ</span> Config Health Checks</h3>
					<p>Validates your configuration and highlights potential issues with clear severity levels and resolution guidance.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<h3><span class="feature-icon">üíæ</span> Automatic Backups</h3>
					<p>Every save creates a timestamped backup so you can always roll back. No data is ever lost.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-card">
					<h3><span class="feature-icon">üìã</span> Merged Config Viewer</h3>
					<p>See the effective configuration with source attribution ‚Äî know exactly which file each setting comes from.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="install">
			<h2>Quick Install</h2>
			<div class="code-block">
				<span class="comment"># Clone and build from source</span><br />
				git clone https://github.com/utensils/fig.git<br />
				cd fig/Fig<br />
				swift build<br />
				<br />
				<span class="comment"># Or open in Xcode</span><br />
				open Package.swift
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			<ul class="footer-links">
				<li><a href="/fig/getting-started/">Documentation</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://github.com/utensils/fig">GitHub</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://github.com/utensils/fig/blob/main/LICENSE">MIT License</a></li>
			</ul>
			<p>Fig is a native macOS app for managing Claude Code configuration.</p>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
